        <updateDate>2019-03-19T21:56:06Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Protecting American Solar Jobs Act </b></p> <p>This bill amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to eliminate tariffs placed on specified imported solar power technology (i.e., crystalline silicon photovoltaic cells). The bill applies retroactively to February 7, 2018. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
